divs: Sighting DetailsWhile sitting in house this morning I glanced out window to North. I saw what was an aircraft at about a 60 angle in the sky more then several miles off at a high altitude. The anomaly did not seem to be moving and I asked my wife to look and tell me what she saw. her head was then in front of me for less then 10 sec. and she said she could not find it. I looked around her and it was gone I searched the area and could not see it anywhere. Hence the term UFO....
trends: There have been no other sightings in Whitleyville

Summary: first thought was an aircraft in the North of my location sighting was for a few seconds
